<br>
Turning softly to Crydee and sighing to herself, she kneels down before him and whispers softly. "This is for your own good, please forgive me..." and with that she cold cocks him with the back of the instrument.<br>
<br>
Crydee falls back into a deep sleep.<br>
<br>
Jzonn raises an eyebrow at Casidy. And Febreeza looks on in amazed shock.<br>
<br>
"He would not have done well in the salty air, and while we will need him for the journey, it would not be good for him to be ill the entire trip." With that Casidy sits down and takes a deep swig of the wine.<br>
<br>
A good vintage, she thinks to herself and passes the bottle to Febreeza.<br>
<br>
"Tell me more of what lies ahead Ranger," Casidy speaks softly to Jzonn.<br>
